id":"af1fdcaf98c4bcbf079ae5f574765325b8cab521","tid":2391993,"uid":51266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T02:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50561f5920be0f1f895d4a46b19044cb65119f1e","tid":2391993,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b86ed2356c8cec87484f7a03507e7b063ca138b","tid":2391993,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4f1aa31d9536d6b865b00b5053398501efa6b2","tid":2391993,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:54:13.000Z","msg":"政府延長電話卡實名登記制度諮詢期至下月20日<br />\n<br />\n政府今日宣布延長電話智能卡實名登記制度的公眾諮詢期至3月20日，讓業界和市民有更多時間研究諮詢文件的內容和建議，並向政府提交意見。<br />\n<br />\n政府於1月30日展開公眾諮詢，建議透過《電訊條例》訂立規例實施電話智能卡實名登記制度，讓電訊商按規例的要求登記、收集和儲存用戶的登記資料，以堵塞目前電話智能卡尤其是預付儲值卡因其匿名性質而造成的漏洞，防止和協助偵查涉及使用電話儲值卡的罪案，並維持市民對本港電訊服務的信心。公眾諮詢期原於2月28日結束。<br />\n<br />\n諮詢文件可在商務及經濟發展局通訊及創意產業科網站（<a href=\"http://www.cedb.gov.hk/ccib/tc/consultations-and-publications/SIM_Chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cedb.gov.hk%2Fccib%2Ftc%2Fconsultations-and-publications%2FSIM_Chi.pdf&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=5622be6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.cedb.gov.hk/ccib/tc/consultations-and-publications/SIM_Chi.pdf</a>）下載。市民可將意見電郵（SIM@cedb.gov.hk）、傳真（2511 1458）或郵遞至香港添馬添美道二號政府總部西翼二十一樓商務及經濟發展局通訊及創意產業科。"},{"pid":"3e8ee1ec376e3386ca673782f5b5bda3f4426457","tid":2391993,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:55:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3daa6c88455f1e7a4aa4e7bf15d6fc8dffbc5a6","tid":2391993,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22bd03c0b4da664ec542cf5271cc567f849cc80","tid":2391993,"uid":80478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d7bcc5d676d6fc53e9d46838a4a1a933e41c8a5","tid":2391993,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee3882c702b97f9453c031f5c6f40f0652d0992","tid":2391993,"uid":284261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:39:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"47ef4da588038ded84bae13e83f0b929eb5bf467","tid":2391993,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c8afb595c96da8748ac623c88e6d0cce960aa4","tid":2391993,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ca6df3ddb9e3e4907ff170946172c89ce5f964